WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:03.321
The FX original series,
The Americans.

00:03.370 --> 00:05.668
The new season,
Wednesdays at 10:00 on FX.

00:08.370 --> 00:09.632
PREVIOUSLY ON
"THE AMERICANS"...

00:09.670 --> 00:11.661
Philip: THERE'S ONE MOVE
WE COULD MAKE.

00:11.710 --> 00:14.031
WE PUT A BUG
IN GAAD'S OFFICE.

00:17.580 --> 00:19.639
HE IS A BRILLIANT PHYSICIST

00:19.680 --> 00:23.810
AND AN ELOQUENT ADVOCATE
FOR THOSE JEWISH REFUSENIKS

00:23.850 --> 00:25.215
STILL TRAPPED
IN THE SOVIET UNION.

00:25.250 --> 00:27.559
WE'RE TAKING THE SCIENTIST.

00:27.590 --> 00:29.729
YOU'RE GONNA SEND ME
BACK TO RUSSIA? IS THAT IT?

00:29.760 --> 00:33.821
HOW CAN I WORK IN A PLACE I'VE
SPENT MY LIFE TRYING TO ESCAPE?

00:33.860 --> 00:36.897
[ Sobbing ] YOU'RE A MONSTER!

00:36.930 --> 00:38.659
THAT STUDENT YOU FOLLOWED

00:38.700 --> 00:40.668
MET WITH EUGENE VENTER FROM
SOUTH AFRICAN INTELLIGENCE.

00:40.700 --> 00:43.168
WE THINK HE'S PLANNING
TO STAGE AN ATTACK.

00:43.210 --> 00:44.837
NCGOBO'S GOING TO SET
ANOTHER MEETING.

00:44.870 --> 00:47.532
WE'RE HOPING VENTER SHOWS UP
TO KILL NCGOBO.

00:48.240 --> 00:50.777
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

00:59.050 --> 01:01.382
[ VEHICLE APPROACHES ]

01:20.280 --> 01:22.202
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

01:22.250 --> 01:25.208
THE THURSDAY MEETING
IS CANCELED, TOO,

01:25.250 --> 01:26.877
UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE.

01:26.920 --> 01:29.445
HAS HE INTERVIEWED
YOU GUYS YET?

01:29.490 --> 01:30.548
NOT YET. YOU?

01:30.590 --> 01:33.115
TWICE.

01:33.160 --> 01:35.458
UH, WHAT DID THEY
ASK YOU ABOUT?
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

01:35.490 --> 01:37.378
HE SAID I COULDN'T SAY.

01:37.430 --> 01:39.250
YOU DON'T SEND SOMEONE
FROM THE OFFICE

01:39.300 --> 01:41.291
OF PROFESSIONAL
RESPONSIBILITY

01:41.330 --> 01:43.389
IF SOMETHING BIG
ISN'T GOING ON.

01:43.430 --> 01:45.967
MARTHA?
YES, SIR?

01:46.000 --> 01:47.558
AGENT TAFFET WOULD LIKE TO SPEAK
WITH YOU.

01:47.600 --> 01:49.238
NOW?

01:49.270 --> 01:50.498
YES.

01:54.140 --> 01:55.835
THANK YOU.

02:00.620 --> 02:04.818
SO, YOU'RE USED TO BEING
ON THE OTHER SIDE OF THIS.

02:06.490 --> 02:08.253
[ SPITS ]

02:08.290 --> 02:11.453
I WAS NEVER
AN INTERROGATOR.

02:11.490 --> 02:14.926
WE CAN MAKE AN OFFER --

02:14.960 --> 02:17.428
$1 MILLION U.S.

02:17.470 --> 02:20.837
AND A NEW LIFE
IN A NEW COUNTRY.

02:22.970 --> 02:25.803
NOT FOR ME.

02:33.520 --> 02:34.976
[ SIGHS ]

02:41.160 --> 02:43.025
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

05:26.990 --> 05:30.983
OUT OF ALL THOSE PEOPLE WITH
ACCESS TO AGENT GAAD'S OFFICE,

05:31.030 --> 05:33.999
DO YOU RECALL ANYONE
BEING IN THERE ALONE?

05:34.030 --> 05:36.794
EVE R?

05:36.830 --> 05:39.799
I'VE BEEN SECRETARY
TO THE SPECIAL AGENT IN CHARGE

05:39.840 --> 05:41.637
FOR THE PAST
SEVEN YEARS, SIR.

05:41.670 --> 05:43.831
WELL, SAY,
IN THE LAST YEAR OR TWO.

05:43.870 --> 05:47.306
WELL, I HAVEN'T REALLY
THOUGHT ABOUT IT.

05:47.340 --> 05:51.299
UH...ME, UM...

05:51.350 --> 05:55.138
THE CLEANING PEOPLE,
OF COURSE.

05:55.180 --> 05:58.479
UM, I GAVE AGENT BREWSTER
A FILE ONCE,

05:58.520 --> 05:59.987
'CAUSE I HAD MY HANDS FULL
AT THE TIME.

06:00.020 --> 06:02.557
AGENT BREWSTER.

06:02.590 --> 06:05.980
HE RETIRED IN '79.

06:06.030 --> 06:08.555
DO YOU PROVIDE AGENT GAAD
WITH OFFICE SUPPLIES?

06:08.600 --> 06:11.160
YES.
UH, PENS, PAPER,

06:11.200 --> 06:14.397
STAPLES, PAPER CLIPS,
THINGS OF THAT NATURE.

06:14.440 --> 06:15.998
AGENT GAAD LIKES TO RUN
A TIGHT SHIP

06:16.040 --> 06:17.667
AS FAR AS OFFICE SUPPLIES
ARE CONCERNED.

06:17.710 --> 06:22.875
DID YOU SUPPLY AGENT GAAD
WITH THIS PEN?

06:22.910 --> 06:25.572
WELL, I DON'T KNOW.

06:25.610 --> 06:27.544
THERE ARE SO MANY
OFFICE SUPPLIES,

06:27.580 --> 06:30.048
PENS IN PARTICULAR,
FLOATING AROUND THE OFFICE,

06:30.090 --> 06:32.012
AND PEOPLE LEAVE THEM
EVERYWHERE.

06:32.050 --> 06:34.018
IT'S VERY ANNOYING.

06:34.060 --> 06:36.551
DID ANYONE GIVE YOU THIS PEN
TO GIVE TO AGENT GAAD?

06:36.590 --> 06:39.058
I DON'T THINK SO.

06:39.090 --> 06:40.523
YOU DON'T THINK SO?

06:40.560 --> 06:42.528
NO.

06:42.570 --> 06:46.392
DID ANYONE ASK YOU TO TAMPER
IN ANY WAY WITH THIS PEN?

06:47.740 --> 06:49.935
NO, SIR.

06:51.410 --> 06:54.868
WERE YOU CHARGED WITH
MAINTAINING AGENT GAAD'S PENS?

06:56.750 --> 07:00.868
KEEPING THEM CURRENT,
WORKING,

07:00.920 --> 07:04.583
FULL OF INK.

07:04.620 --> 07:06.212
NOT REALLY.

07:06.250 --> 07:09.378
IF AGENT GAAD WANTS A PEN,
HE MIGHT ASK ME FOR ONE,

07:09.420 --> 07:11.627
OR GO TO
THE SUPPLY CABINET,

07:11.660 --> 07:13.059
BUT...

07:13.100 --> 07:15.056
THAT PEN -- THAT'S, UH --

07:15.100 --> 07:17.068
THAT'S NOT A SUPPLY PEN...

07:17.100 --> 07:19.796
I DON'T THINK.

07:41.820 --> 07:44.254
I'M COLD.

07:44.290 --> 07:47.589
CAN I HAVE MY COAT?

07:47.630 --> 07:50.428
MAYBE LATER.

07:50.470 --> 07:53.337
RIGHT NOW I NEED
YOUR HELP, TODD.

07:53.370 --> 07:56.601
IF YOU HELP ME,
I WILL HELP YOU.

07:56.640 --> 07:58.631
DOES THAT SEEM FAIR?

08:01.340 --> 08:05.504
HOW LONG HAVE YOU BEEN WORKING
WITH EUGENE VENTER?

08:09.990 --> 08:12.311
ARKADY IVONOVICH?

08:12.350 --> 08:13.681
DA.

09:35.440 --> 09:37.101
[ DIAL TONE ]

09:49.580 --> 09:52.617
[ COUGHING ]

09:57.960 --> 09:59.552
ANYTHING?

09:59.590 --> 10:02.388
[ SIGHS ]
HE'S NOT THE TYPE.

10:02.430 --> 10:05.422
TODD SAYS VENTER HAD HIM
MONITORING ANTI-APARTHEID GROUPS

10:05.470 --> 10:06.596
AROUND THE COUNTRY.

10:06.640 --> 10:08.062
THAT'S ALL?

10:08.100 --> 10:09.965
SO HE SAYS.

10:26.820 --> 10:28.651
[ SIGHS ]

10:31.530 --> 10:33.327
I'M OFF.

10:36.130 --> 10:38.428
CATCHING A FLIGHT
TO CHICAGO.

10:38.470 --> 10:40.438
MEMORIAL SERVICE TOMORROW.

10:40.470 --> 10:41.994
OH, YES.

10:42.040 --> 10:44.600
I'M -- I'M VERY SORRY
ABOUT YOUR FRIEND.

10:44.640 --> 10:47.108
I'LL BE BACK IN THE OFFICE
TOMORROW AFTERNOON.

10:47.140 --> 10:49.938
UH, IF ANYONE NEEDS TO GET AHOLD
OF ME BEFORE THEN,

10:49.980 --> 10:52.448
I'LL BE AT THE BEST WESTERN
IN NAPERVILLE.

10:52.480 --> 10:54.778
I LEFI' THE PHONE NUMBER
ON MY DESK.

10:54.820 --> 10:57.288
OKAY.

10:57.320 --> 11:00.483
YOU OKAY?

11:00.520 --> 11:03.125
YEAH. I JUST, UM, ATE SOMETHING
AT LUNCH.

11:03.160 --> 11:04.627
IT DIDN'T AGREE WITH ME.

11:04.660 --> 11:07.788
MM. WELL, FEEL BE'I'I'ER.

11:07.830 --> 11:09.195
THANK YOU.

11:09.230 --> 11:11.164
HAVE A NICE TIME --
WELL, I'M SORRY.

11:11.200 --> 11:12.326
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.

11:12.370 --> 11:14.190
YEAH. THAN KS.

11:27.920 --> 11:31.481
AGENT ADERHOLT,
IS NOW A BAD TIME?

11:31.520 --> 11:32.987
NO.

11:33.020 --> 11:34.317
WELL, I WONDER IF YOU'D MIND

11:34.360 --> 11:36.009
JOINING ME
IN THE INTERVIEW ROOM.

11:36.060 --> 11:37.857
OKAY.

11:37.890 --> 11:41.826
I'M JUST GONNA GRAB A COFFEE.
CAN I GET YOU SOME?

11:41.860 --> 11:43.566
NO, THANK YOU.

11:50.710 --> 11:54.532
YOU'RE NEW HERE,
AGENT ADERHOLT.

11:54.580 --> 11:55.877
IAM.

11:55.910 --> 11:57.878
MM. [ GULPS]

11:57.910 --> 12:00.014
EXCELLENT COFFEE.

12:00.050 --> 12:03.383
STRONG.

12:03.420 --> 12:06.344
YOU WERE RAISED
IN OAKLAND, CALIFORNIA.

12:06.390 --> 12:08.358
I WAS.

12:08.390 --> 12:10.381
YOUR FATHER WAS A JANITOR.

12:10.430 --> 12:13.228
UH, I'M SORRY.
IS THIS RELEVANT?

12:13.260 --> 12:15.353
YOUR BACKGROUND'S UNIQUE.

12:15.400 --> 12:17.220
INTERESTING.

12:17.270 --> 12:19.898
YES. MY FATHER WAS
A SCHOOL JANITOR.

12:19.940 --> 12:22.363
UH, MY MOTHER LEFI'
WHEN I WAS 5.

12:22.400 --> 12:25.699
I HAVE A YOUNGER BROTHER
IN PORTLAND, OREGON.

12:25.740 --> 12:27.230
I HAVE A DOG, SNUFFY.

12:27.280 --> 12:28.872
I'M SURE IT'S ALL IN THERE.

12:28.910 --> 12:31.378
YOU CLERKED IN
THE SAN FRANCISCO OFFICE

12:31.410 --> 12:33.219
WHEN YOU GRADUATED
HIGH SCHOOL.

12:33.250 --> 12:35.411
YOU FOUND IT TO YOUR LIKING,
I PRESUME?

12:35.450 --> 12:36.747
I LOVED WORKING
FOR THE BUREAU.

12:36.790 --> 12:38.109
STILL DO.

12:38.150 --> 12:40.584
SO YOU WORKED YOUR WAY UP
FROM THERE.

12:40.620 --> 12:44.579
UNDERGRADUATE STUDIES
AT BERKELEY AT NIGHT.

12:44.630 --> 12:46.791
ANOTHER JEWEL
IN THE CROWN...

12:48.830 --> 12:52.061
...OF THE CALIFORNIA STATE
UNIVERSITY SYSTEM.

12:52.100 --> 12:55.297
HOME OF THE FREE-SPEECH
MOVEMENT.

12:55.340 --> 12:56.432
THAT TOO.

12:56.470 --> 12:58.631
MAY I SEE YOUR PEN?

13:05.810 --> 13:08.415
MONT BLANC.

13:08.450 --> 13:11.248
IT WAS A GIFT
FROM MY WIFE --

13:11.290 --> 13:13.087
EX-WIFE,
AS I'M SURE YOU KNOW.

13:13.120 --> 13:14.758
I WAS ALWAYS LOSING THEM.

13:14.790 --> 13:17.429
SHE THOUGHT I WOULD TAKE BETTER
CARE OF AN EXPENSIVE PEN.

13:17.460 --> 13:18.927
WELL, SHE WAS RIGHT.

13:18.960 --> 13:21.997
ABOUT MANY THINGS.

13:27.640 --> 13:30.962
OTHERS HAD A LESS DIFFICULT
PATH HERE.

13:33.310 --> 13:36.507
ARE YOU ASKING
IF I'M RESENTFUL?

13:37.880 --> 13:39.643
I'M NOT.

13:39.680 --> 13:42.319
I DON'T SEE MYSELF AS A VICTIM,
AGENT TAFFET.

13:42.350 --> 13:44.284
I GOT A LOT
OF OPPORTUNITIES HERE

13:44.320 --> 13:46.618
I WOULDN'T HAVE GOTTEN
ANYWHERE ELSE.

13:46.650 --> 13:49.619
DO YOU THINK OTHER PEOPLE HERE
RESENT YOU...

13:49.660 --> 13:52.481
FOR BEING NEW?

13:54.830 --> 13:58.960
WELL, BEING NEW
ISN'T A BAD THING --

13:59.000 --> 14:01.662
NEW BEGINNINGS,
NEW BLOOD.

14:01.700 --> 14:04.533
I DON'T THINK MUCH
ABOUT THE REST OF IT.

14:06.010 --> 14:08.376
[ RA'I'TLING ]

14:16.020 --> 14:17.544
GET UP.

14:42.040 --> 14:43.849
[ GUN COCKS ]
NO, NO, MAMA.

14:43.880 --> 14:45.507
I CAME ALL THIS WAY.

14:45.550 --> 14:47.871
THEY KILLED MY BROTHER.

14:47.920 --> 14:51.708
ONE DAY, THEY'RE GOING
TO KILL ME...

14:51.750 --> 14:54.059
PROBABLY MY BOYS.

15:01.060 --> 15:03.893
WE HAVE A WAY
OF DOING THINGS.

15:17.280 --> 15:21.046
YOU ALREADY HAVE
YOUR COUNTRY.

15:21.080 --> 15:23.412
YOU CAN'T UNDERSTAND.

15:26.790 --> 15:28.758
[ OBJECT CLANGS ]

15:31.760 --> 15:34.297
[ GRUNTING ]

15:37.470 --> 15:41.429
YOU ARE GUILTY OF CRIMES AGAINST
THE PEOPLE OF SOUTH AFRICA.

15:41.470 --> 15:43.734
SAYS WHO?

15:43.770 --> 15:45.909
THE A.N.C.?!

15:45.940 --> 15:48.636
THE BLOODY
KAFFIR COMMUNISTS!

15:48.680 --> 15:51.808
YOU'RE A CRIMINAL.

15:51.850 --> 15:53.477
YOU ARE THE ENEMY
OF SOUTH AFRICA,

15:53.520 --> 15:55.909
TO WHAT'S BEEN BUILT WITH
AFRIKANER SWEAT AND BLOOD!

15:55.950 --> 15:58.487
YOUR SENTENCE IS DEATH!

15:58.520 --> 16:00.988
YOU BLACKS --
YOU ARE BEHOLDEN

16:01.020 --> 16:04.148
TO YOUR KAFFIR-BOETIE
COMMUNIST MASTERS!

16:04.190 --> 16:07.250
THESE PEOPLE -- THEY DON'T GIVE
A BLOODY SHIT ABOUT YOU!

16:07.300 --> 16:11.760
THEY WANT THE GOLD,
THE DIAMONDS, THE LAND!

16:11.800 --> 16:14.462
[ LIGHTER CLICKS ]

16:14.500 --> 16:17.264
OH, MY GOD! NO! NO!

16:17.310 --> 16:20.438
OH! OH, JESUS!

16:20.480 --> 16:23.142
[ SCREAMING ]

16:41.830 --> 16:43.491
[ WHIMPERING ]

17:09.520 --> 17:13.058
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

18:12.250 --> 18:15.219
PLEASE. I'M SORRY.
PLEASE DON'T DO THAT TO ME.

18:15.260 --> 18:16.887
I FEEL BAD FOR YOU.

18:16.920 --> 18:18.956
YOU GOT IN OVER YOUR HEAD,

18:18.990 --> 18:22.050
AND I CAN SEE
HOW THAT CAN HAPPEN.

18:22.100 --> 18:24.398
[ SIGHS ]

18:24.430 --> 18:26.421
BUT YOU LIED TO ME.

18:29.300 --> 18:32.599
DON'T WORRY.
WE'RE NOT GONNA DO THAT TO YOU.

18:32.640 --> 18:35.108
THAT'S A HORRIBLE WAY
TO DIE.

18:39.780 --> 18:42.476
WE'LL JUST PUT A BULLET
IN YOUR HEAD.

18:42.520 --> 18:44.249
IT'LL BE OVER LIKE THAT.

18:44.290 --> 18:47.259
[ Crying ] I'LL TELL YOU
ANYTHING YOU WANT.

18:47.290 --> 18:49.758
BUT THAT'S THE THING, THOUGH,
ISN'T IT, TODD?

18:49.790 --> 18:52.258
I MEAN, HOW WILL I KNOW
IF IT'S THE TRUTH?

18:52.290 --> 18:55.123
WELL, IT IS, I SWEAR!

18:56.830 --> 19:00.596
WHEN DID VENTER REALLY WANT
FROM YOU?

19:00.640 --> 19:03.939
HE SAID THINGS
WEREN'T GOING WELL.

19:03.970 --> 19:05.107
"THINGS"?

19:05.140 --> 19:07.108
THAT THE
ANTI-APARTHEID MOVEMENT

19:07.140 --> 19:08.778
WAS GAINING GROUND
IN THE US.

19:08.810 --> 19:10.949
SO, TODD, WHAT DID HE WANT
YOU TO DO?

19:10.980 --> 19:13.312
TO SET A BOMB
ON THE G.W. CAMPUS!

19:18.820 --> 19:22.950
HE WANTED IT TO GO OFF
AT A MEETING OF THE TRUSTEES.

19:22.990 --> 19:25.959
THE G.W. HAS A LOT OF MONEY
INVESTED IN COMPANIES

19:25.990 --> 19:28.026
DOING BUSINESS
IN SOUTH AFRICA.

19:28.060 --> 19:32.190
THE STUDENT GROUPS PROTESTING
APARTHEID WOULD BE BLAMED.

19:32.230 --> 19:34.960
A MAJOR VICTORY
FOR SOUTH AFRICA

19:35.000 --> 19:38.367
AND A BIG SETBACK
FOR THEIR ENEMIES, HE SAID.

19:38.410 --> 19:40.674
AND YOU AGREED TO DO IT?

19:42.840 --> 19:45.638
YES.

19:45.680 --> 19:48.046
BUT I DIDN'T DO IT.

19:48.080 --> 19:50.139
I DIDN'T DO IT.

19:50.180 --> 19:53.684
VENTER GAVE ME THE BOMB,
AND I NEVER SET IT.

19:53.720 --> 19:57.053
I NEVER PLACED IT!

19:57.090 --> 20:00.423
I COULDN'T!
I WAS AFRAID!

20:03.870 --> 20:05.861
WHERE IS THE BOMB?

20:07.700 --> 20:09.531
IN MY DORM.

20:43.940 --> 20:45.908
COME ON.

20:47.780 --> 20:50.749
[ MAN SPEAKING RUSSIAN ]

22:25.010 --> 22:26.159
[ SIGHS ]

23:16.060 --> 23:18.949
[ SIGHS ]

23:56.760 --> 23:58.318
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

24:01.800 --> 24:04.598
IT WAS WHERE HE SAID
IT WOULD BE.

24:07.310 --> 24:11.974
IF IT HAD GONE OFF, IT WOULD
HAVE KILLED A LOT OF PEOPLE.

24:12.010 --> 24:15.411
BUT IT DIDN'T.

24:15.450 --> 24:16.974
[ GUN COCKS ]

24:17.020 --> 24:18.817
HE'S JUST A KID.

24:18.850 --> 24:21.080
HE WANTED TO KILL ME,

24:21.120 --> 24:24.089
AND MANY, MANY MORE,
BUT NOW HE'S JUST A KID TO YOU?!

24:24.130 --> 24:26.280
YOU SAW HIM BACK THERE.
HE'S NOT VENTER.

24:26.330 --> 24:28.093
HE CAN'T STOMACH THIS.

24:28.130 --> 24:29.927
HE'S GOING TO GO RIGHT BACK
TO DOING WHAT HE WAS DOING!

24:29.960 --> 24:31.598
HE TOLD US
WHAT WE NEEDED TO KNOW.

24:31.630 --> 24:32.790
TO SAVE HIS OWN LIFE!

24:32.830 --> 24:34.764
AFTER WHAT HE'S SEEN TODAY,
HE'S DONE!

24:34.800 --> 24:36.267
YOU DON'T KNOW PEOPLE
LIKE HIM!

24:36.300 --> 24:38.131
HE CAN'T IDENTIFY US.

24:40.640 --> 24:43.131
LET'S GIVE HIM THIS CHANCE.

24:48.150 --> 24:49.708
[ TODD SHIVERING ]

25:23.080 --> 25:27.688
[ ENGINES TURNS OVER ]

25:27.720 --> 25:29.517
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

25:32.760 --> 25:34.193
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

25:40.940 --> 25:42.191
[ SIGHS ]

25:52.780 --> 25:54.372
[ DOOR OPENS ]

27:52.170 --> 27:54.161
YOU GOT TIME.

27:57.840 --> 28:00.001
YOUR WIFE IS AT HOME NOW.

28:02.840 --> 28:05.308
YEAH, I THINK SO.

28:05.350 --> 28:09.309
SAFE AND SOUND.

28:09.350 --> 28:13.184
SOMETIMES I CAN'T SEE
MY WIFE'S FACE.

28:15.060 --> 28:19.485
WELL, I CAN SEE HER,
WORKING WITH THE CHILDREN,

28:19.530 --> 28:24.820
BUT I CAN'T
PICTURE HER FACE.

28:24.870 --> 28:30.194
YOU HAVEN'T SEEN HER
IN A LONG TIME.

28:35.710 --> 28:38.099
MAYBE SHE HAS ANOTHER MAN.

28:39.610 --> 28:43.512
I COULDN'T BLAME HER.
SHE'S A VERY GOOD WOMAN.

28:43.550 --> 28:47.384
FORGETTING IS NOT ALWAYS
A BAD THING.

28:51.430 --> 28:56.527
BEING MARRIED
AND BEING AT WAR

28:56.560 --> 28:59.393
DO NOT ALWAYS GO TOGETHER.

29:09.580 --> 29:11.707
SAFE TRAVELS.

29:11.750 --> 29:14.913
AND YOU, COMRADE.

29:27.430 --> 29:31.594
[ CAR DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

29:49.450 --> 29:51.589
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

29:51.620 --> 29:52.917
HOW'S IT GOING?

29:52.950 --> 29:55.418
IT'S BEEN
A PRODUCT IVE DAY.

29:55.460 --> 29:57.928
I'LL BE IN FIRST THING
IN THE MORNING.

29:57.960 --> 30:01.259
I HAVE A FEW THINGS I'D LIKE
TO GO OVER WITH YOU THEN,

30:01.300 --> 30:03.256
FOR CLARIFICATION.

30:03.300 --> 30:05.621
YES, OF COURSE.

30:07.970 --> 30:10.837
I FEEL LIKE I'VE BEEN DRINKING
FROM A FIRE HOSE.

30:10.870 --> 30:12.963
SO MUCH TO ABSORB.

30:13.010 --> 30:14.170
ANY SURPRISES?

30:14.210 --> 30:16.098
THERE ARE ALWAYS SURPRISES.

30:16.140 --> 30:19.439
DID YOU EVER CONSIDER
INSTALLING SECURITY CAMERAS

30:19.480 --> 30:20.674
IN YOUR OFFICE?

30:20.710 --> 30:21.972
NO.

30:22.020 --> 30:24.011
FACING THE DOOR.

30:24.050 --> 30:28.350
WE WOULDN'T BE HAVING THIS
EASTER-EGG HUNT IF YOU HAD.

30:28.390 --> 30:30.278
I MEAN, I'M NOT SAYING
THAT YOUR NEGLIGENCE

30:30.320 --> 30:32.288
RESULTED IN THE KGB GETTING
ACCESS INTO THE BUREAU.

30:32.330 --> 30:35.128
BUT YOU'RE NOT PREPARED
TO SAY IT DIDN'T?

30:35.160 --> 30:37.993
HAVE A GOOD EVENING,
AGENT GAAD.

30:41.340 --> 30:43.638
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

30:43.670 --> 30:46.639
Man: HERE ON BBC NEWS
AT THE TOP OF THE HOUR.

30:46.670 --> 30:47.807
IN AFGHANISTAN,

30:47.840 --> 30:49.876
SOVIET SCORCHED-EARTH TACTICS

30:49.910 --> 30:53.300
HAVE YET TO DETER
AHMAD SHAH MASSOUD'S MILITIA,

30:53.350 --> 30:55.818
WHICH HAVE REPORTEDLY INCREASED
THEIR RANKS

30:55.850 --> 30:57.715
FOLLOWING
AN AGGRESSIVE OFFENSIVE

30:57.750 --> 30:59.217
OF HIGH-ALTITUDE BOMBING

30:59.250 --> 31:01.059
AND LONG-RANGE
ARTILLERY SHELLING.

31:01.090 --> 31:03.479
AN ESTIMATED 80%
OF THE INFRASTRUCTURE

31:03.520 --> 31:06.887
HAS BEEN DESTROYED OR DAMAGED
IN THE PANJSHIR VALLEY REGION,

31:06.930 --> 31:08.397
LEAVING REFUGEES SCA'I'TERED

31:08.430 --> 31:10.022
THROUGHOUT THE NEIGHBORING
PROVINCES.

31:10.060 --> 31:11.197
[ RADIO CLICKS OFF ]

31:11.230 --> 31:13.221
NEWS?

31:13.270 --> 31:17.866
AFGHANISTAN, WAR.

31:25.710 --> 31:28.349
YOUR SON --

31:28.380 --> 31:31.213
WHAT'S HIS NAME?

31:34.390 --> 31:36.210
MISHA.

31:48.300 --> 31:51.428
OH, MARTHA, WHERE'S THAT
CONTINGENCY REPORT I ASKED FOR?

31:51.470 --> 31:52.903
IT'S IN THE MAIL ROBOT.

31:52.940 --> 31:55.374
I TRIED TO GET IT OUT,
BUT IT'S JAMMED AGAIN.

31:55.410 --> 31:57.230
OH, FOR CRYING OUT LOUD,
GIVE ME THE KEYS.

32:08.420 --> 32:10.081
[ ROBOT BEEPING ]

32:13.660 --> 32:15.423
[ KEYS RATTLING ]

32:17.760 --> 32:19.466
GOD DAMN IT TO HELL!

32:19.500 --> 32:21.764
[ RAPID BEEPING ]

32:30.640 --> 32:31.971
[ SIGHS ]

32:32.950 --> 32:34.076
HEY, SWEETIE.

32:34.120 --> 32:36.111
HI.

32:38.850 --> 32:42.251
BREAKFAST FOR DINNER?
[ CHUCKLES ]

32:42.290 --> 32:43.655
I MADE HENRY SOME EGGS.

32:43.690 --> 32:46.079
WHAT'S HE UP TO?

32:46.130 --> 32:47.654
I DON'T KNOW.

32:47.690 --> 32:50.329
PLAYING SOME ELECTRONIC GAME
THAT HE GOT FROM DOUG.

32:50.360 --> 32:52.760
YOU DOING SCHOOL WORK?

32:52.800 --> 32:54.267
NO. JUST...

32:54.300 --> 32:56.962
INTERESTED.

32:57.000 --> 32:58.262
IN WHAT?

32:58.310 --> 33:00.164
YOUR FRIEND...

33:00.210 --> 33:02.804
GREGORY.

33:06.210 --> 33:08.178
I WENT TO THE LIBRARY

33:08.220 --> 33:12.441
AND LOOKED UP SOME REPORTS
FROM WHEN HE WAS...

33:12.490 --> 33:14.651
MM.

33:17.320 --> 33:21.290
THE NEWSPAPER SAID
HE WAS A DRUG DEALER.

33:21.330 --> 33:24.993
HIS LIFE WAS COMPLICATED.

33:25.030 --> 33:26.793
IT WAS HARD.

33:26.830 --> 33:29.799
BUT HE --

33:29.840 --> 33:33.628
HE NEVER STOPPED FIGHTING
FOR WHAT WAS RIGHT.

33:33.670 --> 33:39.848
SO, WAS HE A CRIMINAL,
OR WASN'T HE?

33:43.680 --> 33:46.911
THINGS AREN'T THAT SIMPLE.

33:50.090 --> 33:53.685
AND...

33:53.730 --> 33:55.721
I MEAN, YOU KNOW THAT.

33:55.760 --> 33:59.662
YOU'RE ALREADY FIGHTING
AGAINST INJUSTICE.

33:59.700 --> 34:02.498
WHO ARE YOU
FIGHTING AGAINST?

34:02.540 --> 34:05.998
COUNTRIES, GOVERNMENTS,

34:06.040 --> 34:08.031
PEOPLE WHO MAKE LAWS.

34:10.040 --> 34:12.406
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

34:12.450 --> 34:15.669
I GUESS.

34:15.720 --> 34:18.188
BUT [SIGHS]

34:18.220 --> 34:21.678
YOU CAN'T JUST GO ROB BANKS
AND THINGS.

34:21.720 --> 34:23.859
NO, YOU CAN'T.

34:23.890 --> 34:25.721
OF COURSE NOT.

35:32.530 --> 35:34.157
NYET.

35:56.150 --> 35:58.789
[ DOOR OPENS ]

35:58.820 --> 36:00.788
ANYBODY HOME?

36:00.820 --> 36:03.118
HEY. OH!

36:03.160 --> 36:06.459
I SEE THE PARTY STARTED
WITHOUT ME.

36:06.490 --> 36:11.291
I HAVE HAD A CRAZY DAY.

36:11.330 --> 36:13.969
HAD A MEETING
WHICH GOT CANCELED,

36:14.000 --> 36:18.130
BUT...THEY FORGOT TO TELL ME
ABOUT IT.

36:18.170 --> 36:20.138
UGH.

36:20.170 --> 36:21.535
ANYWAY. ..

36:21.580 --> 36:23.309
HI.

36:23.340 --> 36:26.309
[ SIGHS ]

36:26.350 --> 36:31.845
I MET A MAN NAMED
WALTER TAFFET YESTERDAY.

36:33.690 --> 36:35.988
WHO'S HE?

36:36.020 --> 36:38.682
Taffet.

36:40.530 --> 36:42.851
WELL, HE'S YOU.

36:44.100 --> 36:46.660
I [SIGHS]

36:46.700 --> 36:49.191
[Voice breaking ]
THEY FOUND THE PEN.

36:52.240 --> 36:55.676
WHO ARE YOU?

36:55.710 --> 36:58.543
MARTHA...

37:03.620 --> 37:07.112
WHO ARE YOU, CLARK?

37:19.570 --> 37:22.869
I'M YOUR HUSBAND,

37:22.900 --> 37:25.630
THE MAN YOU MARRIED...

37:28.240 --> 37:33.246
...WHO LOVES YOU MORE
THAN YOU WILL EVER KNOW.

37:36.250 --> 37:38.411
[ Sobbing ] OH, GOD.

37:42.420 --> 37:44.456
WHAT HAVE I DONE?

37:44.490 --> 37:47.084
[ SOBS ]

37:47.130 --> 37:49.928
OH, MY GOD.

37:49.960 --> 37:52.724
WHAT HAVE I DONE?
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

37:52.770 --> 37:56.888
MARTHA, MARTHA, YOU --
YOU FELL IN LOVE --

37:56.940 --> 37:58.567
WE -- WE FELL IN LOVE.

37:58.610 --> 38:01.408
IS THIS FOR REAL?
I MEAN, IS ANY OF THIS TRUE?

38:01.440 --> 38:04.238
WE ARE WHAT'S REAL,
AND THAT'S ALL THAT MATTERS.

38:04.280 --> 38:07.078
W-- THAT'S --
THAT IS WHAT IS TRUE.

38:07.110 --> 38:09.943
PLEASE, CLARK.

38:09.980 --> 38:12.585
PLEASE DON'T LIE TO ME,

38:12.620 --> 38:14.611
BECAUSE I CAN'T TAKE IT
IF YOU'RE GONNA LIE TO ME.

38:14.660 --> 38:16.252
I'M -- I'M NOT --
I'M NOT LYING TO YOU.

38:16.290 --> 38:18.622
MARTHA,
I'M NOT LYING TO YOU.

38:18.660 --> 38:20.787
LISTEN TO ME.
I AM TELLING YOU THE TRUTH,

38:20.830 --> 38:25.961
AND EVERYTHING I AM ABOUT TO SAY
IS THE TRUTH.

38:26.000 --> 38:29.993
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

38:30.040 --> 38:32.759
WHEN WE FIRST MET,

38:32.810 --> 38:35.108
I-I DIDN'T WANT TO FALL IN LOVE
WITH YOU,

38:35.140 --> 38:37.108
BUT I DID.

38:37.140 --> 38:38.277
[ CRIES ]

38:38.310 --> 38:40.278
AND NOW YOU MEAN...

38:40.310 --> 38:43.973
SO MUCH TO ME.

38:44.020 --> 38:45.612
YOU HAVE TO BELIEVE THAT.

38:45.650 --> 38:47.288
YOU ARE ONE OF THE MOST...

38:47.320 --> 38:52.121
TRUE AND HONEST
AND GOOD WOMEN

38:52.160 --> 38:53.684
I HAVE EVER KNOWN.

38:59.530 --> 39:03.034
I LOVE YOU...

39:03.070 --> 39:07.131
AND I WOULD DO ANYTHING
FOR YOU...

39:07.170 --> 39:09.309
[ SNIFFLES ]

39:09.340 --> 39:12.377
...TO PROTECT YOU.

39:16.350 --> 39:17.840
[ SOBBING LIGHTLY ]

39:20.390 --> 39:23.188
IS THAT ENOUGH...

39:23.220 --> 39:25.051
[ GASPING ]

39:29.860 --> 39:35.036
OR DO YOU NEED MORE
THAN THAT?

39:54.420 --> 39:56.251
[ SOBBING ]

40:17.410 --> 40:20.243
THANK YOU.
I HAVE SOMETHING FOR YOU.

40:35.100 --> 40:37.056
IS SHE --

40:37.100 --> 40:38.965
SHE'S A FIGHTER.

40:40.930 --> 40:42.090
THANK YOU.

40:42.140 --> 40:43.630
NOT AT ALL.

40:54.680 --> 40:59.583
THIS THING WITH KIMBERLEY
HAS BEEN HARD ON PHILIP.

40:59.620 --> 41:02.088
SHE'S VERY YOUNG.

41:02.120 --> 41:05.453
HE KNOWS -- WE BOTH KNOW

41:05.490 --> 41:07.082
THAT MAINTAINING ACCESS

41:07.130 --> 41:10.099
TO THE C.I.A. AFGHAN GROUP
IS CRITICAL,

41:10.130 --> 41:11.620
ESPECIALLY RIGHT NOW.

41:16.470 --> 41:19.109
I HAVE A FAVOR TO ASK.

41:19.140 --> 41:21.836
SURE. SIT DOWN.

41:33.350 --> 41:35.955
I WANT YOU TO SEE
WHAT YOU CAN DO

41:35.990 --> 41:38.686
TO HELP PHILIP'S SON
IN AFGHANISTAN

41:38.730 --> 41:41.119
TO GET HIM HOME.

41:41.160 --> 41:44.823
I DIDN'T REALIZE YOU KNEW
ABOUT THE BOY.

41:44.870 --> 41:47.668
HE TOLD ME.

41:50.370 --> 41:53.464
[ SIGHS ]

41:53.510 --> 41:56.707
I'LL DO WHAT I CAN.
